name: Llama Park #13
description:
Bow to QueenTweet, the royal influencer of Llama Park! With a golden crown sparkling and a regal gaze, this purple-skinned girl llama drapes in a royal robe against a grayish-blue backdrop. An ENFP, she rules Twitter with viral posts that charm the masses. 'Tweet puff puff!' she declares, spreading joy, but spits with royal sass when displeased. Her bubbly charm and majestic vibe make her the park’s social queen!
描述：向Llama Park的皇家网红QueenTweet致敬！金冠闪耀，目光威严，这只紫肤女羊驼披着皇袍，站在灰蓝色背景前。ENFP的她用病毒式推文统治Twitter，魅力无穷。‘推特噗噗！’她宣布，散播欢乐，不悦时皇室傲娇吐口水。她的活泼魅力和高贵气质让她成为公园的社交女王！
